    "In Fig. 4, Fig.",
    "4 Overview of application domains.",
    "For each application domain (y-axis), we show the number of occurrences of keywords belonging to its macro-area (x-axis)",
    "we show the application domains with more than 10 index keyword occurrences.",
    "We group the keywords into macro areas, such as in \"Energy\" we include keywords like \"energy\", \"energy conservation\", \"energy consumption\", etc., in \"Electric energy\" we group keywords such as \"electric energy storage\", \"electric load dispatching\", \"smart grid\", etc."
